parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door ajar sensor can cause the interior lights to stay on, drain the battery, and prevent the doors from locking, which can lead to safety hazards and distractions while driving.
symptoms: The door ajar warning light stays on
interior lights stay on
alarm goes off randomly
doors do not lock while driving
doors unlock themselves while driving
and the child safety lock feature does not function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and hydraulic system can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the radio to turn off, the climate control system to malfunction, and the battery to drain, which can lead to safety hazards and distractions while driving.
symptoms: The radio turns off
the climate control system malfunctions
the heater engages to high
the battery drains
and the alarm system goes off randomly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering assist can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn or seize, making it difficult to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The power steering assist fault warning light illuminates
the steering wheel becomes difficult to turn or seizes
the vehicle is difficult to steer
the power steering assist message is displayed on the instrument panel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door latch system can cause the doors to remain unlocked, even when they are closed, which can lead to accidents or injuries, especially when the vehicle is in motion. Additionally, the constant illumination of interior lights can drain the battery, leaving the vehicle stranded.
symptoms: The door ajar warning light illuminates
interior lights remain on
doors cannot be locked
alarm sounds randomly
and battery drains.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power liftgate can cause it to unexpectedly come down, hitting occupants or objects, which can lead to injuries or accidents.
symptoms: The power liftgate comes down unexpectedly
even when it is not in use.
